    CR -->|permissions| DSCs
    CR -->|permissions| DSCIs
    CR -->|permissions| InferenceServices
    CR -->|permissions| ModelRegistries

    %% Role permissions (namespace-scoped)
    R -->|permissions| AcceleratorProfiles
    R -->|permissions| OdhApplications
    R -->|permissions| OdhDocuments
    R -->|permissions| QuickStarts
    R -->|permissions| RoutesNS
    R -->|permissions| CronJobs
