    R -->|permissions| Templates
    R -->|permissions| ServingRuntimes

    %% Monitoring access
    CRMonitoring -->|Prometheus metrics| PrometheusAccess[Prometheus queries<br/>9091/TCP]

    %% Auth delegator
    CRAuthDelegator -->|token validation| TokenReview[TokenReview API<br/>OAuth delegation]

    %% Image puller
    CRImagePuller -->|image access| ImageAccess[Image Registry<br/>pull images]

